# Environment files. `.env` is intentionally TRACKED (demo-build needs a
# live ASTRO_API_KEY bundled as an asset so the reviewer can boot the APK
# without manual Settings entry). Variant overrides like `.env.local`
# stay ignored. See README §Live mode and lib/main.dart.
.env.local
.env.dev
.env.staging
.env.prod
.env.*.local

